    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I mean, with this html:\n\n``` html\n<div id=\"search-parent\" class=\"user-style\">\n  <input type=\"text\" id=\"search\" />\n</div>\n```\n\nAnd this js:\n\n``` javascript\nsearch.addWidget(\n  instantsearch.widgets.searchBox({\n    container: '#search',\n    placeholder: 'Search for products'\n  })\n);\n```\n\nor this one:\n\n``` javascript\nsearch.addWidget(\n  instantsearch.widgets.searchBox({\n    container: '#search-parent',\n    placeholder: 'Search for products'\n  })\n);\n```\n\nThe following markup should be generated:\n\n``` html\n<div id=\"search-parent\" class=\"user-style\">\n  <div class=\"ais-search-box\">\n    <input type=\"text\" id=\"search\" placeholder=\"Search for products\" class=\"ais-search-box--input\" />\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n\n(Currently the `<div class=\"ais-search-box\">` is missing, and that is what I want to add)\n",
    "created_at": "2015-10-26T14:00:59Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/352#issuecomment-151142350",
